contentment,

1236
01:18:12,187 --> 01:18:16,687
Among your acquaintances
and many relatives.

1237
01:18:18,026 --> 01:18:21,029
We congratulate,

1238
01:18:21,154 --> 01:18:23,990
Mrs. Jensen turns 80 today,

1239
01:18:24,115 --> 01:18:26,867
Long live she.

1240
01:18:26,993 --> 01:18:29,912
Now and forevermore!

1241
01:18:34,209 --> 01:18:36,169
There are still 2 verses.

1242
01:18:36,294 --> 01:18:39,588
I think, that's enough now. I
have to eat something now.

1243
01:18:39,714 --> 01:18:41,298
Stay calm and sit still!

1244
01:18:43,218 --> 01:18:46,221
Madam, You are
light as a feather.

1245
01:18:46,346 --> 01:18:47,805
Are you sitting
comfortably, Mother?

1246
01:18:47,931 --> 01:18:51,726
That's the 80th now. The
75th was just recently.

1247
01:18:51,851 --> 01:18:54,061
No, not with your back outwards.

1248
01:18:57,857 --> 01:19:01,485
I always say, Food keeps
body and bowl together.

1249
01:19:01,611 --> 01:19:03,446
Soul! Body and soul!

1250
01:19:03,571 --> 01:19:05,531
Interesting, that
women can't conduct.

1251
01:19:05,657 --> 01:19:07,659
Why can't I conduct?

1252
01:19:07,784 --> 01:19:10,495
- I am Pastor Hummel.
- Never mind, never mind!

1253
01:19:10,620 --> 01:19:13,331
Here, here, right
here in the middle.

1254
01:19:13,456 --> 01:19:15,332
Or no! To the head end!

1255
01:19:15,458 --> 01:19:18,461
Mother, we carry you, 
wherever you want.

1256
01:19:18,586 --> 01:19:20,921
<i>Light... like a feather.</i>

1257
01:19:21,047 --> 01:19:23,132
May we sit next to you, Mother?

1258
01:19:23,258 --> 01:19:24,717
Sit where you want.

1259
01:19:24,842 --> 01:19:27,928
Dieter, for you the ladies
of the choir have set a place.

1260
01:19:28,054 --> 01:19:31,724
This is my place. I always
sit next to my husband.

1261
01:19:31,849 --> 01:19:34,893
(Mimics)" "I always
sit next to my husband!

1262
01:19:44,279 --> 01:19:47,282
(Grandma Jensen) Now we eat.

1263
01:19:47,407 --> 01:19:49,409
otherwise I can become
very uncomfortable.

1264
01:20:27,322 --> 01:20:29,073
(Giggles foolishly)

1265
01:20:35,288 --> 01:20:37,373
- Do you belong to the family?
- No.

1266
01:20:37,498 --> 01:20:38,832
Lucky pig.

1267
01:20:38,958 --> 01:20:40,918
What's that?

1268
01:20:41,044 --> 01:20:42,503
- Herb cream soup.
- Ugh!

1269
01:20:43,921 --> 01:20:46,089
That's herb cream with tarragon.

1270
01:20:46,215 --> 01:20:48,675
Food is for sustenance. One
does not speak about it.

1271
01:20:48,801 --> 01:20:51,386
Hellmuth and I eat
sufficiently, but simply.

1272
01:20:51,512 --> 01:20:54,264
Now the mayor is talking!
Lütje, what is it now?

1273
01:20:54,390 --> 01:20:58,727
I thought, after the... after
the main course, I thought.

1274
01:20:58,853 --> 01:21:02,773
(Incomprehensible mumbling)

1275
01:21:08,071 --> 01:21:09,405
(Snickered)

1276
01:21:13,534 --> 01:21:15,494
(Glass clinking)

1277
01:21:15,620 --> 01:21:17,872
Hellmuth wants to say something.

1278
01:21:17,997 --> 01:21:19,081
My dear God.

1279
01:21:19,207 --> 01:21:21,167
Esteemed Mrs. Mama,

1280
01:21:21,292 --> 01:21:23,419
my highly esteemed
ladies and gentlemen,

1281
01:21:23,544 --> 01:21:28,044
Dear family! 80
years! 80 lived years,

1282
01:21:29,759 --> 01:21:31,719
of which 47 were marriage
years, the most beautiful.

1283
01:21:31,844 --> 01:21:33,804
That's new to me.

1284
01:21:33,930 --> 01:21:38,430
Anyway...so...Hedwig and I,

1285
01:21:38,893 --> 01:21:41,896
we have been in our
6-year engagement period

1286
01:21:42,021 --> 01:21:44,523
mutually exclusive

1287
01:21:44,649 --> 01:21:49,028
and are now already rewarded
daily for so many years

1288
01:21:49,153 --> 01:21:52,781
through our harmonious coexistence,
for each other and...

1289
01:21:52,907 --> 01:21:56,785
Uh, yeah. Man and woman
are they... Or something like that:

1290
01:21:56,911 --> 01:21:58,871
Man and woman
complement each other.

1291
01:21:58,996 --> 01:22:03,000
If I may just say this freely.

1292
01:22:03,126 --> 01:22:07,626
I wouldn't be what I am
without Hedwig, and Hedwig...

1293
01:22:07,755 --> 01:22:10,758
Even if we mistakenly
differ in opinion,

1294
01:22:10,883 --> 01:22:15,095
have we become particularly fond of
each other. I believe it will be clear ...

1295
01:22:15,221 --> 01:22:18,307
Listen here! Hedwig!
 - ...what I'm trying to say.

1296
01:22:18,433 --> 01:22:21,227
We may be proud of each other.

1297
01:22:21,352 --> 01:22:24,355
Our sympathy goes
out to all couples,

1298
01:22:24,480 --> 01:22:28,609
to those this is
obviously not granted.

1299
01:22:28,734 --> 01:22:33,234
Maybe they'll finally
toast to my health. Cheers!

1300
01:22:33,406 --> 01:22:37,906
- (All) Long live she...
- It won't be sung anymore!

1301
01:22:38,619 --> 01:22:41,079
(All fall silent abruptly)

1302
01:22:41,205 --> 01:22:43,040
Now my bag has fallen down!

1303
01:22:43,166 --> 01:22:45,126
I'll be screwed.

1304
01:22:48,546 --> 01:22:50,965
My husband prepared
for Mother's birthday.

1305
01:22:51,090 --> 01:22:53,050
You and your
husband, this milk roll,

1306
01:22:53,176 --> 01:22:56,220
You are so wonderful,
that it chokes me up!

1307
01:22:56,345 --> 01:22:59,598
- No, how ordinary!
- Can I help you, darling?

1308
01:22:59,724 --> 01:23:01,600
Maybe they will reappear.

1309
01:23:01,726 --> 01:23:04,770
Mom asks when you'll
be back upstairs for dinner.

1310
01:23:04,896 --> 01:23:09,396
Renate has expressed
herself very badly about us.

1311
01:23:09,567 --> 01:23:12,069
When it comes to the relationship 
between man and woman, we

1312
01:23:12,195 --> 01:23:14,071
won't be trifled with.

1313
01:23:14,197 --> 01:23:16,657
And if Renate is so ill-mannered, 
she has a problem.

1314
01:23:16,782 --> 01:23:19,534
- Esteemed guests...
- We have always noticed,

1315
01:23:19,660 --> 01:23:22,412
- that your marriage lacks warmth.
- Inner warmth.

1316
01:23:22,538 --> 01:23:24,498
Well! We're missing her.

1317
01:23:24,624 --> 01:23:28,628
And unfortunately, we are also lacking
your deep affection for each other.

1318
01:23:28,753 --> 01:23:30,880
This wonderful and yet
so humble happiness.

1319
01:23:31,005 --> 01:23:33,215
And the cheerfulness
coming from within.

1320
01:23:33,341 --> 01:23:36,677
The cheerful basis for
harmonious coexistence.

1321
01:23:40,223 --> 01:23:44,143
- Hedwig...listen up! Hedwig!
- Did you hear that, Mother?

1322
01:23:44,268 --> 01:23:47,896
Hedwig, the mayor
is speaking with you!

1323
01:23:48,022 --> 01:23:50,149
(Slurring) Hedwig,
you are the sharpest,

1324
01:23:50,274 --> 01:23:54,069
what I have ever encountered
between Heringsdorf and Borkum.

1325
01:23:54,195 --> 01:23:57,406
Mr. Lütje, you just said
something very vulgar!

1326
01:23:57,532 --> 01:24:02,032
The mayor certainly
wanted to do me a favor.

1327
01:24:02,286 --> 01:24:04,621
I am not of that opinion.

1328
01:24:04,747 --> 01:24:06,957
And we are never of
different opinion.

1329
01:24:07,083 --> 01:24:09,543
Then please join my opinion.

1330
01:24:09,669 --> 01:24:12,797
- Do you belong to the family?
- No.

1331
01:24:12,922 --> 01:24:15,925
I apologize for the
lewdness of my wife!

1332
01:24:17,593 --> 01:24:21,471
(Dieter) "She spoke to him, 
she sang to him,

1333
01:24:21,597 --> 01:24:23,181
And he was lost to her spell.

1334
01:24:23,307 --> 01:24:26,268
Half she pulled him,
half he sank down,

1335
01:24:26,394 --> 01:24:28,979
And he was never seen again."

1336
01:24:29,105 --> 01:24:30,689
And then?

1337
01:24:30,815 --> 01:24:33,067
Nothing more.

1338
01:24:33,192 --> 01:24:36,778
(Everyone is talking at once)

1339
01:24:36,904 --> 01:24:38,238
Something is broken between us!

1340
01:24:38,364 --> 01:24:40,366
You have taken the innocence
from our togetherness!

1341
01:24:40,491 --> 01:24:42,826
What? I didn't
understand the last part.

1342
01:24:42,952 --> 01:24:45,955
Did you actually
speak with me just now?

1343
01:24:46,080 --> 01:24:48,373
<i>No, I was just
talking to myself.</i>

1344
01:24:48,499 --> 01:24:50,292
But now you've said something.

1345
01:24:50,418 --> 01:24:53,129
- I wouldn't know what.
- You said,

1346
01:24:53,254 --> 01:24:55,047
that you were
talking to yourself.

1347
01:24:55,172 --> 01:24:56,965
- Yes.
- Like I said.

1348
01:24:57,091 --> 01:25:00,302
Pastor! Say something,
for heaven's sake.

1349
01:25:00,428 --> 01:25:01,804
My dear friends...

1350
01:25:01,929 --> 01:25:04,681
What a wonderful party!

1351
01:25:04,807 --> 01:25:08,185
- No one is listening anyway. 
 - ...no idea about women!

1352
01:25:08,311 --> 01:25:11,022
How do you want to know
if I can conduct or not?

1353
01:25:11,147 --> 01:25:14,150
I don't care whether
you can conduct or not.

1354
01:25:14,275 --> 01:25:15,985
(Laughs exaggeratedly)

1355
01:25:16,110 --> 01:25:20,610
I'm missing something about
you. I don't know exactly what.

1356
01:25:22,116 --> 01:25:25,744
Hedwig, you are the
hottest, who ever...

1357
01:25:25,870 --> 01:25:27,830
Should I serve the Pear Helene?

1358
01:25:27,955 --> 01:25:30,207
- What's that?
- Heinrich!

1359
01:25:30,333 --> 01:25:32,626
This is an apple
compote with cream.

1360
01:25:32,752 --> 01:25:35,421
2 times.

1361
01:25:35,546 --> 01:25:38,382
(Conducting a march
with a chicken bone)

1362
01:25:38,507 --> 01:25:42,552
Could it be that
I... that I have been

1363
01:25:42,678 --> 01:25:45,681
- Not always quite...
- Yes.

1364
01:25:45,806 --> 01:25:48,809
If I now try even harder...

1365
01:25:48,934 --> 01:25:52,020
No, Heinrich,
please! Only not that.

1366
01:25:53,856 --> 01:25:56,900
But there must be something
provided for these cases!

1367
01:25:57,026 --> 01:25:59,361
Rules of thumb or
something like that.

1368
01:25:59,487 --> 01:26:03,407
And what if we now
do something together?

1369
01:26:03,532 --> 01:26:06,284
What should we do together?

1370
01:26:06,410 --> 01:26:08,495
(Mrs. Lohse) It should
be something sensible.

1371
01:26:08,621 --> 01:26:11,665
(Mr. Lohse) Meaningful!
Meaningful it must be!

1372
01:26:34,271 --> 01:26:38,771
(Extremely discordant
recorder playing)

1373
01:27:04,385 --> 01:27:08,472
(Cheerful marching music
overlays the false flute)

